CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Au Revoir - Pittsburgh Gays said "au revoir" to their guests Sunday at a brunch held at the handsome Aliquippa home of Dr. ad[sic] Mrs. Max Johnson, left. Right, Dr. and Mrs. Carroll Holmes.  She's a Steel City Gay- All Photos by Harris"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Dr. and Mrs. Max Johnson, and Dr. and Mrs. Carroll Holmes, standing underneath awning at Johnson's home for Gay Northeasterner farewell brunch
